#                                                                                #
# Welcome to Nomads! The only (known) text-based Nomad simulator, created by an  #
# actual nomad.                                                                  #
#                                                                                #
# This game simulates life on the road while living in a vehicle.                #
#                                                                                #
# Feel free to experiment with different vehicles and job combinations to        #
# discover your style! Each combination comes with unique strengths and          #
# weaknesses.                                                                    #
#                                                                                #
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ #
#                                   OBJECTIVES                                   #
#   1) Try not to die or get stuck. 💀                                           #
#   2) Try not to run out of food or water. 🥫 / 🚰                              #
#   3) Try not to run out of fuel or electricity. ⛽ / 🔋                        #
#   4) Outfit your rig with solar, wind and other improvements. ☀️  / 🍃 / 🛰️    #
#   5) NPCs will have quests for you, if you can find them. 🧔 / 🧑 / 👱         #
##################################################################################

